    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Reaper uses Wraith Form or Shadow Step to get in close undetected, then leans on The Reaping&#39;s lifesteal to win point-blank shotgun trades against grouped enemies.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>His shotguns fall off hard at range, so poke comps and long sightlines neutralize him almost completely unless he can close the distance first.</p>\n"
